{"tid":1644651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打！求保護！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:00:22.000Z","uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf969e29ada474f038b83898ccd6c523437247d0","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"我係一個要返 Shift 嘅絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近見好多當街打人 捉人 拉人 揼人落街<br />\n夜晚返屋企果時真係好驚<br />\n加上黨鐵幫手宵禁 條街就更少人 ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打 可唔可以請大家幫幫手<br />\n夜晚食飽飯 約朋友去散步 練下跑步<br />\n或者去公園坐陣吹水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打落去 就約多幾個朋友 安全啲！！<br />\n<br />\n條街多咗人 佢哋就無位落手 <br />\n就算唔好彩俾狗吠 都有人幫手拍下片呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家已經無警狀態 唯有靠大家守望相助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油！！"},{"pid":"34dbdedaf989c2b5fb5afc34865a5e4969984ebb","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"ec31d77a49a1290f30217ebd685b0f15aa2d4c69","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29587102519d5f8929bfa3717c76f714bd879516","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9b27d05fc550a863f5e36bfa812d7ed93ffe406","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96f7df7438858a02febc8bcbd3fa94986bd24c5f","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b132cbde36191522adc8b97b6efa3dd8e69d8544","tid":1644651,"uid":238022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:59:49.000Z",